133
00:10:00,210 --> 00:10:01,850
Nevidel si,
že je pred tebou auto?!

134
00:10:01,850 --> 00:10:04,020
Ak si ma nevidel,
je načase si kúpiť kontaktné šošovky!

135
00:10:04,020 --> 00:10:06,990
